  * feature: Add STDIN Mode to process_perfdata.pl ( Robert Steininger )
  * Bugfix:  XSS issue fixed by Mikael Falkvidd. This issue was detected by Peter Ã–sterberg at Hexbit AB in a security assessment of op5 Monitor 6.3 on assignment by op5 AB. 

